<devicesets>
<deviceset name="789317893" prefix="T">
<description>&lt;b&gt;WE-AGDA Auxiliary Gate Drive Transformer Automotive&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/b&gt;for SiC-MOSFET and IGBT
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Characteristics 
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;Interwinding capacitance down to &lt;3 pF
&lt;br&gt;Tiny surface mount EP7 package
&lt;br&gt;Dielectric insulation up to 4 kV AC
&lt;br&gt;Basic insulation for 568 Vrms / 800 Vpk
&lt;br&gt;AEC-Q200 qualification
&lt;br&gt;Common control voltages for SiC MOSFET’s
&lt;br&gt;Up to 6 W output power
&lt;br&gt;Wide range input voltages 7 V to 36 V
&lt;br&gt;Different unipolar and bipolar voltages available
&lt;br&gt;Operating temperature: -40 °C up to +130 °C

&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Applications 
&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Motor inverters
&lt;br&gt;OBCs
&lt;br&gt;Active power factor correction
&lt;br&gt;Flyback, LLC, Half- and Full Bridge topologies
&lt;br&gt;SiC-MOSFET based power converter
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.we-online.com/components/media/o893879v209%20multi-78931xxxx.jpg" title="Enlarge picture"&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.we-online.com/components/media/o893879v209%20multi-78931xxxx.jpg" width="320"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;
Details see: &lt;a href="www.we-online.com/catalog/WE-AGDA/?utm_source=eagle_model&amp;utm_medium=description_link&amp;utm_campaign=eisos_eagle"&gt;www.we-online.com/en/components/products/WE-AGDA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;

Created by Ella 2026-05-12 &lt;br&gt;
2026 (C) Würth Elektronik</description>
